{"tid":478462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八人隨木船漂流到日本　稱來自北韓","createTime":"2017-11-24T05:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T09:56:38.000Z","uid":37554,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"39d193675c38c80cecb3c2ec4db74f0dcc3ab07c","tid":478462,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本秋田縣警方正調查隨一艘木船漂流到當地的八名男子，他們聲稱來自北韓。<br />\n<br />\n秋田縣警方是在昨晚十一時半左右接到居民報警，說由利本莊市海岸附近有可疑人士，警員到場後發現一艘木船，船上有八名男子，操類似韓語的語言，將他們帶返警署。<br />\n<br />\n他們聲稱來自北韓，捕魚時船隻發生故障因此漂流到日本，日本當局正辨認他們的身分，研究歸國安排。<br />\n<br />\n秋田縣位於本州西北部，與北韓相隔着日本海。"},{"pid":"334039fbdd16b498a74498648c0fad76895ff123","tid":478462,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"故障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f3e1e5d8651d00af8aa42247bfa2f5e3688e0e","tid":478462,"uid":82382,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"研究歸國安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33abe4f640ab90a4d0c387ffd8596decc87d63f0","tid":478462,"uid":90890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究歸國安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n67了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e1b5ca9189cb9532dc09ebb671e296405bd6d8","tid":478462,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fca570185c98bfcf756d1760c8d1dd4b7374435","tid":478462,"uid":5502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"根本係間諜"},{"pid":"877051ee3677b072171cd8d03a7eddaf642717f5","tid":478462,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB